<p><a href="/7523/1213/2/en">Delegative democracy: democracy is the best of the 21st century</a></p>
<p>
Delegative democracy - voting is an effective model for collective decision-making in large communities. It combines the advantages of direct and representative democracy, representing a truly democratic voting system, which allows people to vote on a particular issue or directly transmit your voice trustee.
